<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: white; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #9EFF00; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #000; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
    .body { padding: 30px; color: #333; }
    .info-box { background: #f9f9f9; border-left: 4px solid #9EFF00; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #9EFF00; color: #000; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background: #111; color: #888; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>WG Tech Solutions</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Thank You, <%= fullname %>! 🎉</h2>
      <p>We have received your proposal and will get back to you shortly.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p><strong>📧 Your Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
        <p><strong>💰 Your Budget:</strong> $<%= budget %></p>
        <p><strong>📋 Status:</strong> Pending Review</p>
      </div>

      <p>You can track your proposal status by logging into your account:</p>
      <a href="<%= adminLink %>" class="btn">Access Your Account</a>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p><strong>🔐 Your Login Credentials:</strong></p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
        <p><strong>Password:</strong> <%= password %></p>
      </div>

      <p>Our team will review your proposal and contact you within 24-48 hours.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br><strong>WG Tech Solutions Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2024 WG Tech Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>info@wgtecsol.com | wgtecsol.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>